summary: This mod adds a room in the back of breezehome with 2 mannequins 2 chests and a place to hang your weapons.
descriptionHtml:
A small room added in the back of breezehome with 2 mannequins 2 chests and a place to hang your weapons. This mod is for people that want breezehome to stay small but with some more functionality.

There are 2 versions the normal version (v1.0) and the version V1E. V1E adds a enchanting table to the room.

INSTALLATION

Just add the files to the data folder or use nexus mod manager

UNINSTALLATION

Move all of you items out of the chests and mannequins if you have too much you can use a console commmand (TGM unlimted carry weight)
author: Sthij
